data.description: Come live the Coastal Lifestyle in Award Winning Founders Pointe. As you walk into this home, you will be greeted by warm sunshine and an open floor plan. Looking for a master suite on the first floor? Come see this beautiful master suite with dual vanity and large shower with bench. Every room has so much space and natural light. The kitchen is where you will enjoy family gatherings and dinner parties.   Live the Good Life with Founders Pointe resort style amenities include a Residents’ Club with lakefront swimming pool and 112' water slide, 844' observation pier offering panoramic views of Batten Bay and the James River, 3 miles of biking/leisure trails and sidewalks, Children’s playground and sand volleyball court, and Full-time activities director coordinating year-round events for all ages.
